<div style="background-color: #ffffff; margin: 20px auto; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); max-width: 600px">
<h1 style="color: #333333;">Event Registration Confirmation</h1>
<p>Thank you for registering for the upcoming event, <strong>{!Event__c.Event_Name__c}</strong>!</p>
<p style="color: #555555;">Dear {!Contact.FirstName},</p>
<p>We are excited to confirm your participation in the event. Below are the event details:</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Event Name:</strong> {!Event__c.Event_Name__c}</li>
<li><strong>Event Date:</strong> {!Event__c.Event_Date__c}</li>
<li><strong>Event Time:</strong> {!Event__c.Start_Time__c}</li>
<li><strong>Location:</strong> {IEvent__c.Location__c}</li>
<li><strong>Description:</strong> {Event__c.Description__c}</li>
</ul>
