<p>We look forward to seeing you at the event!</p>

<p>Best regards,</p>
<p>{!Account.Name}</p>
<p>{!Account.PersonEmail}</p>
<p>{!Account.Phone}</p>

<div style="margin-top: 20px; font-size: 12px; color: #777777;">
